comments: Zeller (CHA) makes incidental contact to Randle's (NYK) arm after the release of his jump shot attempt.
Noel (NYK) makes incidental contact with Bridges' (CHA) arm as he attempts to get to the loose ball during the rebound.
Rozier (CHA) veers into Burks' (NYK) path and delivers contact at the end of his drive that affects Burks' ability to defend.
McDaniels (CHA) extends his arms into Noel's (NYK) body and dislodges him during the pick.
McDaniels (CHA) makes marginal contact with Burks' (NYK) arm during his drive and does not affect his SQBR.
Bridges (CHA) moves laterally along Burks' (NYK) path and makes marginal contact with his body during the driving shot attempt.
McDaniels (CHA) splits his feet at the start of his dribble.
Randle (NYK) gathers the ball and comes to legal jump stop.
Noel (NYK) jumps vertically and maintains a legal vertical position as he absorbs the contact to Rozier's (CHA) body during the driving shot attempt.
Zeller (CHA) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Randle (NYK) and the contact is marginal.
Randle (NYK) briefly places his hand to Rozier's (CHA) front at the start of the drive and does not affect his SQBR.
McDaniels (CHA) dislodges Burks (NYK) from his position during the rebound.
McDaniels (CHA) slightly extends his arm into Randle's (NYK) body during the screen and does not affect his ability to defend.
Burks (NYK) briefly grasps Bridges' (CHA) arm during the pick and does not affect his FOM.
Burks (NYK) slightly extends his arm into McDaniels' (CHA) body and does not dislodge him from his legally obtained position during the rebound.
